@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jpupwe(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v1 + 0.51)) / tmp)
    tmp = (wp.exp(0.17) - 0.80)
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.53)) * (v2 + wp.sin(v2 + 0.33)))
    tmp = (0.28 + wp.cos(tmp))
    tmp = ((tmp * v0) * wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.16)))
    data[tid] = v0
